Dogs are healing!!!! 

Recently my neighborhood that is predominantly black received a dog park. Something I don’t see in many black neighborhoods. We have a group chat for the dog park and one of the dog parents said “I thank the universe for this support group everyday” I couldn’t help but think about all the therapeutic spaces that aren’t put in (or taken out) black neighborhoods. Something as simple as a dog park can create a community of healing.
